org.restcomm.sbc.chain

Interface ProcessorChain

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProcessorChainImpl, UpstreamRegistrarRequestProcessChain, UpstreamRegistrarResponseProcessChain

    public interface ProcessorChain
    A ProcessorChain is a component of a chain of responsibility responsible in the construction of the chain of Processors that will interact in the transformation of the message. it enqueues processors and controls the chain life-cycle.
